0:09:09.980,0:09:14.080
and for Germany as well a year later.

0:09:14.080,0:09:19.700
As for me, I commit myself to making your work, the work of your working group

0:09:19.700,0:09:25.910
and the UN mandate a topic for national debate on which citizens will give their opinion.

